The thermal lining also gives a more compressive feel when worn. If you would prefer a more relaxed fit for all day wear we suggest you go up a size. If you prefer a more snug and firm fit, we suggest your usual size. PLEASE NOTE: Due to the nature of brushed fleece, these leggings can be prone to pilling so we recommend washing yours inside out in our Active Washbag on a delicate cycle to extend it's life.
